8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Beautiful.ai and Gamma share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Ai Generation. On the other hand, Gamma uniquely offers Responsive, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Beautiful.ai holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Gamma scores 8/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
