c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Beautiful.ai is best suited for sales teams, consultants, business professionals, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Gamma, meanwhile, shines for startup pitches, internal docs, quick presentations, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, Beautiful.ai describes itself as \"AI presentation maker that automatically designs stunning slides.\" Gamma, established in 2020, positions itself as \"AI-powered tool for creating presentations, documents, and webpages.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Gamma** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (9 vs 8), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Beautiful.ai is a poor choice — far from it. Beautiful.ai excels in its own right, particularly for sales teams and consultants.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value generate full presentations from prompts, go with Gamma. If ai auto-designs slides beautifully matters more to you, Beautiful.ai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
